Bokeem Woodbine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bokeem_Woodbine 0 Bokeem Woodbine (born April 13, 1973) is an American actor. For his role as Mike Milligan on the second season of Fargo, he won a Black Reel Award and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award and a Critics' Choice Television Award. He also portrayed Daniel in season 2 of the WGN series Underground and Herman Schultz/Shocker in the film Spider-Man: Homecoming. Bokeem_Woodbine ( born April_13_,_1973 ) is an_American_actor .
